ENERGY DRAIN

Usage       : cast 'energy drain' <victim>
Accumulative: -
Duration    : Instantaneous
Save        : Versus spell for half damage.

Drains one level from a PC, or does 100 hp of damage to an NPC.  Lost
levels loose max hit points, and practices.  Beware of monsters with
level draining ability.  Be aware that this spell is evil.

